::Firearm::

"Don't worry about it," says a confused Firearm shutting off the map 
of the world, "We'll try scanning his spark signature. He'll turn up."

He looks at her, wondering if any remains of Trainer programming were 
still there. "Hey, do you have any more Trainer programming left in 
ya? It could help us get him back."
